name: Verify that the Underwriter Manager column is shown in mentioned Quote Overview reports whereever there is a Underwriter column next to it and populate the Underwriter Manager values

testSteps.description: 1: Verify that the Underwriter Manager column is shown in mentioned Quote Overview reports whereever there is a Underwriter column next to it and populate the Underwriter Manager values ({Reports=Lost Quotes})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And select Reports 'Lost Quotes' from Quotes
And select Reports 'Quotes Pending Issuance' from Quotes
When user select Underwriting Overview 'Underwriting Overview' from VIEW
Then the field 'UNDERWRITER MANAGER' should be displayed next to 'UNDERWRITER NAME'

dataTable.scenarioOutline:
Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And user Navigates to Reports
And select Quotes 'Quotes' from Reports
And select Reports '<Reports>' from Quotes
And select Reports 'Quotes Pending Issuance' from Quotes
When user select Underwriting Overview 'Underwriting Overview' from VIEW
Then the field 'UNDERWRITER MANAGER' should be displayed next to 'UNDERWRITER NAME'
